body:
Add BreadcrumbList JSON-LD schema to every HTML file under v3/ that does not already have it.

Format for each page:
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://crashycrash.github.io/offbeat-website/v3/"},
    {"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"[Page Name]","item":"[full URL]"}
  ]
}

Add inside a script type application/ld+json block. Do NOT remove existing schemas. Report which files were updated.

Add SiteNavigationElement JSON-LD schema to v3/index.html.

Schema to add:
{
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'SiteLinksSearchBox',
  'url': 'https://crashycrash.github.io/offbeat-website/v3/',
  'potentialAction': {'@type': 'SearchAction', 'target': 'https://crashycrash.github.io/offbeat-website/v3/faq.html', 'query-input': 'required name=search_term_string'}
}

Also add ItemPage schema to each non-index v3 page that does not already have a page-level schema.

Report which specific files and schemas were added.
